💕 GALLON-TINES GIVEAWAY 💕 Every February 13th, we celebrate ""Gallon-tines"" Day to share the love with you all! Enter for a chance to win a SWEET prize from Milo's and make this Gallon-tines Day one to remember. Details below! 👇

To enter, make sure you:
❤️ LIKE this post
❤️ FOLLOW @drinkmilos
❤️ TAG your galentine or valentine in the comments (every tag is an entry)
*
PRIZE PACKAGE:
Five (5) lucky winners will receive TWO Milo's Tumblers, and TWO FREE GALLONS of Milo’s (one set to keep and one to share).
*
Winner will be notified on 2/17/25. Good luck!
*
Please be advised the winners will be contacted by direct message from the @drinkmilos account, and we will never ask for credit card information for a giveaway.
*
NO PURCHASE NECESSARY. VOID WHERE PROHIBITED. Open only to US/DC winner(s) must be 18+. Ends 2/16/25, 11:59PM EST. Winners will be contacted via direct message. This giveaway is in no way sponsored, endorsed, administered by, or associated with Instagram. See Official Rules at the link in bio.
